{"tid":2268702,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"鬼滅之刃｜8套AV另類山寨　蝴蝶姊妹丼、《你的名字》繩結變捆綁","createTime":"2020-11-03T04:04:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-03T04:05:28.000Z","uid":147522,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"f0cbd1612987d42c9be684da1318c0e9d032927b","tid":2268702,"uid":147522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T04:04:10.000Z","msg":"《鬼滅之刃 無限列車篇》劇場電影版屢破紀錄，成為最快達100億日圓票房的動畫，AV界也看到了《鬼滅之刃 》的潛力，同步推出AV版「無限發射篇」。其實過去也有不少「另類山寨」的作品，連新海誠、JOKER、復仇者都逃不出魔掌。<br />\n<br />\n其實《鬼滅之刃 》一早已經出過AV版，今次「無限發射篇」係添食之作，玩食字之餘，參演女優陣容上升至4人，亦更加豪華。過去不少AV廠商都以cosplay為主打，產出不少經典另類山寨作品，拍得好可滿足觀眾，拍得不好的話，分分鐘鹹片變笑片。<br />\n<br />\n小夫和胖虎的哆啦AV夢，令不少人童年回憶崩壞，不過對於某一部份網民來說，只可算是笑料一則，因為我們的童年，一早已經充滿陰影...小時候看動畫，卻被當中的暗黑情節嚇個半死，要甚就看完心頭像是壓了一塊大石，久久不能釋懷，這樣的情況大家多多少少都遇過，《開罐》整理了6個小時候心靈受創的名場面，在大家的傷口上灑鹽。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5iUFJ4b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5iUFJ4b.jpg&h=01031176&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Cqh0J4c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCqh0J4c.jpg&h=ad1133f6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nWcW1QT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnWcW1QT.jpg&h=5b3c6808&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0wB1tvU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0wB1tvU.jpg&h=6d8e551c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BPxW1QV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBPxW1QV.jpg&h=fe71c92a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2LKRQKg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2LKRQKg.jpg&h=892db284&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/z1Ea6hB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fz1Ea6hB.jpg&h=677d74e7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8LrEfaX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8LrEfaX.jpg&h=944a656f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hh7so4i.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fhh7so4i.jpg&h=252eb23e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"11d334c2bda95e7231a85f41bddf8a4bfbb8f9df","tid":2268702,"uid":13013,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T04:05:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}